The paper discusses real-time data analysis and management, which is a common topic in database systems (cs.DB) and data structures (cs.DS). The proposal for integrating robust streaming into SQL involves syntax and semantics, which are related to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper also mentions implementations in Apache Calcite, Apache Flink, and Apache Beam, which are machine learning frameworks (cs.LG).
